				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Actually, the PPU is <em><span style="text-decoration: underline">always</span></em> running. For each CPU cycle, the PPU runs for 3 cycles. Pixels are rendered only if background or sprites are enabled. Keep track of the PPU cycle and scanline - you need it for VBlank, NMI... as I already mentioned here.</div>

					
							<br /><br />
